316
00:19:43,760 --> 00:19:44,880
Thank you, Boss.

317
00:19:50,280 --> 00:19:51,160
Open it.

318
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,040
Can I?

319
00:19:53,040 --> 00:19:53,640
