394
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:45,800
Damn. A death threat?

395
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:46,800
Yup.

396
00:25:47,560 --> 00:25:50,240
Got it. I give you my word.

397
00:25:50,280 --> 00:25:53,200
