423
00:27:33,880 --> 00:27:35,640
This might be a bit outdated now,

424
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:37,080
but…

425
00:27:37,080 --> 00:27:38,320
could I ask for your autograph?

426
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:40,320
As a memento.

427
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:42,800
Gladly.

428
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:45,880
I follow your work too, Mr. Hojun.

429
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:49,840
It’d be an honor to work with you.

430
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:59,480
