441
00:28:56,360 --> 00:28:57,320
What's wrong?

442
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:09,040
Don't tell me that woman is also—

443
00:29:09,040 --> 00:29:11,560
Today’s not my day.
I’m out, take care of the rest.

444
00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:13,760
Hey, wait up!

445
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:15,920
You’re really gonna ditch me? Come on.

446
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:18,320
After all I’ve done,
you still say I’m ditching you?

447
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:21,080
