struggle all on your own.

448
00:29:21,560 --> 00:29:22,680
Don’t be mad, man.

449
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:25,400
Seriously, though.

450
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:27,200
No offense,

451
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:28,800
