549
00:38:19,680 --> 00:38:20,680
Calm down, please.

550
00:38:21,320 --> 00:38:22,240
Go away!

551
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:23,640
Please, get in the car.

552
00:38:23,640 --> 00:38:24,960
Boss, stay still.

553
00:38:25,960 --> 00:38:27,320
Boss.

554
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,200
